            "hint": "Add class=\"navbar navbar-dark bg-dark\" and class=\"navbar-brand\".",
            "solutionCode": "<nav class=\"navbar navbar-light bg-light\">\n  <a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"#\">Navbar</a>\n</nav>"
